-- Monitise names former Visa executive as co-CEO
-- By Aastha Agnihotri in Bangalore
-- Wed Jun 04, 2014 02:22AM EDT
-- None



June 4 (Reuters) - Mobile banking technology company Monitise Plc <MONI.L> said it appointed Elizabeth Buse, a former Visa Inc <V.N> executive, as co-chief executive with immediate effect.

